snagit is a simple screen capture software that allows you to capture either videos or pictures of your desktop, edit, and share quickly. snagit also has a large library of drawing tools that allows you to grab your audience's attention with shapes, callouts, highlighting, step-by-step labels, and much more.some common uses of snagit include:it is very important to keep accessibility in mind when using snagit to ensure that all images whether placed on the web, word documents, or pdf files are accessible by including an alternative text (or alt text). alternative text provides users the ability to have a text description of what an image is showing.feel free to visit the websites below which will provide additional information about alternative text and how to apply alternative texts to microsoft word and pdf files.please use theon-demand video request formto request an introduction to snagit tutorial video or an advanced snagit features video. feel free to reach out toecampus@sjsu.edufor any questions or assistance after viewing the on-demand videos.please fill out thesnagit request formbelow if you would like to receive a copy of snagit.download adobe readerphone:408-924-2337email:ecampus@sjsu.edulocation: irc, room 206ecampus, irc206instructional resource centersan jose state universityone washington squaresan jose, ca 95192-0026